content: For a Westerner to trash Western culture is like criticizing our nitrogen/oxygen
  atmoshere on the grounds that it sometimes gets windy, and besides, Jupiter's is
  much prettier. You may not realize its advantages until you're trying to breathe
  liquid methane.
